"Our ANC brothers will not field a candidate here while we will not field one in Matungu," he said.
Ms Wambilianga said they will not allow Lusweti's funeral to be turned into a political battle ground.
She further asked residents to adhere to the Health ministry's guidelines for preventing the spread of Covid-19.
Mr Waluke said he is now the acting MP Kabuchai Constituency, which was split from his Sirisia Constituency.
He promised a fitting send-off for Lusweti.
